title: Kolsai Lakes
description: Kolsai is a system of lakes located 300 km South East of Almaty, on Kungei Alatau mountain ridge which is Northern part of Tien Shan. Lower Kolsai, Mynzholkiat and Upper Kolsai are the most prominent lakes of Kolsai and major touristic spot.
